After 6 months 2G was restored in Kashmir few day ago with access to only some white listed websites. Social media has been banned here.
People here are using VPN to access banned websites . Today I got VPN and it took me 3 hours to connect and when I visited youtube ,this tribute to Habba Khtoon welcomed me.
It filled my eyes . Every one in Kashmir relates to this 'Song of separation'...
